Description: VITOS base layer (users, PAM, consent banner, auditd skeleton)
 Provides the vitos-students and vitos-admins groups, default accounts,
 sudoers policy, login consent banner, Plymouth boot theme, LightDM
 branding, and the minimal auditd ruleset that the vitos-monitor package
 extends.
